high_descs: Turn left then walk straight turn left stand in between the tv and table
Face the table and pick up the pen
Turn left then head to the side table beside the couch
Put the pen in the bowl
Pick up the bowl with pen
Turn left then walk straight turn right on the tv stand
Put the bowl with pen on the left side of the tv stand
anns.task_desc: Put the bowl with pen on the tv stand

high_descs: Go forward to the wall, hang a left, go to the far end of the black table between the TV and the red chair and turn to face the table.
Pick up the blue and white pen that is on the table to the left.
Turn to the left, go forward, hang a left and go to the round black table at the end of the room.
Put the pen in the bowl that is on the table.
Pick up the bowl from the table.
Turn around, hang a right, go to the table with the TV on it.
Put the bowl on the left side of the table in front of the TV.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl containing a pen on a table.

high_descs: Turn left, go past the table on the left, turn around to face the pen on the side of the table.
Pick up the pen on the table.
Turn around, bring the pen to the small round table in the corner on the left.
Put the pen in the bowl on the table.
Pick up the bowl with pen on the table.
Bring the bowl with pen to the TV stand on the left.
Put the bowl with pen on the TV stand.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl with pen on the TV stand.
